---
title: Caribbean Lentil & Beef Pie with Creamy Coconut Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing plant-based pie! A coconutty, Caribbean-spiced lentil filling meets a golden potato topping for a dish that's equally wholesome and delish.
